headline: Celsius Stock Is Upgraded. Why These Analysts Say the Energy Drink Maker Is a Buy.
summary: Celsius Holdings  got a jolt on Monday after analysts at TD Cowen upgraded the stock to Buy from Hold and lifted their price target to $55 a share from $37.  Shares of the energy drink maker jumped 6.8% to $43.97.  Celsius  has been on a rollercoaster over the last year.
